{"tid":1212300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一次物資請包括埋屎袋","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T10:46:16.000Z","uid":15309,"like":361,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"af06b83d17ddc21ed2612f18e9c7155929fb8f4c","tid":1212300,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:03:00.000Z","msg":"每人一袋集腋成裘<br />\n掉到佢地全身都係<br />\n冇得沖涼又冇得換 <br />\n殺傷力又冇咁大<br />\n係比較冇咁暴力而又解決到佢地裝備充足呢樣問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先要屎加適量尿溝埋<br />\n用兩至三個袋裝 打死結<br />\n到要用果陣隨手一掉就搞掂<br />\n又可以遮左佢地既眼罩 擋視線<br />\n<br />\n共勉之各位"},{"pid":"71ac7e453d58ef76e1b25323f92287c9d52b8b77","tid":1212300,"uid":15309,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"用長繩綁三角鐵馬<br />\n我見有啲推完出去就掉左 好浪費<br />\n只要有兩條長繩綁住鐵馬<br />\n推完出去之後<br />\n由後面既人拉返返黎<br />\n前面既人慢慢退<br />\n就可以保存好進攻防守既工具<br />\n又唔會突然冇左一兩個三角鐵馬令防線崩口<br />\n覺得可行既推比更多人睇<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"f1b8dd313561314dbde6f77f6a49c72fff0f1144","tid":1212300,"uid":225871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2085473461f5e4a004bbc4bac76f62b3e5119fbc","tid":1212300,"uid":64601,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"邊個會運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9063bfe7af0755f4061b4d0b17b734f5b7ed680b","tid":1212300,"uid":259098,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"用氣球會唔會更好，易爆啲"},{"pid":"8f10b84aa58b7c3ece5c2a3ada22277c31f8940b","tid":1212300,"uid":37869,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"雖然我覺得冇咩可能真係有屎<br />\n但如果真係有的話<br />\n鐵馬淋屎點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要清路障無可避免要接觸到路障"},{"pid":"b1e17429309b015da692ed2b74678f190849ea9e","tid":1212300,"uid":69